.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-LINE-HEIGHT 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
line\-height \- Compute line\-height values for a given font size
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBline\-height\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIFONT_SIZE\fR] [\fINAME\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Compute line\-height values for a given font size
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIFONT_SIZE\fR] [default: 16]
Font size in pixels (defaults to 16)
.TP
[\fINAME\fR]
Show only a single named ratio (tight, snug, normal, relaxed, loose, golden)
